es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.group.evaluation
Class NormGroupOutcomes

java.lang.Object
  es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.group.evaluation.NormGroupOutcomes

public class NormGroupOutcomes
extends java.lang.Object

Class containing information about the norm groups that each agent has complied/infringed, and the agent contexts in which those norms are applicable. Furthermore, the class has information about the number of conflicts that arose after agents complied/infringed the norms

Author:
"Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"
